  --- broker 6126 c. The consumer group maps directly to the same Apache Kafka concept. Partitioning also maps directly to Apache Kafka partitions as well. The binder currently uses the Apache Kafka kafka-clients version 3.1.0 . This client can communicate with older brokers (see the Kafka documentation), but certain features may not be available. For example, with versions earlier than 0.11.x.x, native headers are not supported. Also, 0.11.x.x does not support the autoAddPartitions property. Usage Configuration Options .cls-1h{fill:none;stroke:#000;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:2px;} spring-cloud-stream Stable 5.0.2 4.3.3 4.2.3 4.1.6 Snapshot 5.0.3-SNAPSHOT 4.3.4-SNAPSHOT 4.2.4-SNAPSHOT Related Spring Documentation Spring Boot Spri
